text: Renganaden Seeneevassen State Secondary School is a state school based in Port Louis, Mauritius. The school is named after Renganaden Seeneevassen, the first Mauritian Minister of Education . == See also == * Education in Mauritius * List of secondary schools in Mauritius == References == Category:Schools in Mauritius Category:Port Louis Category:Girls' schools in Mauritius
